HOW TO REPORT prime n:
    REPORT n>=2 AND NO d IN {2..floor (root n)} HAS n mod d=0

HOW TO RETURN digit.sum n:
    SELECT:
        n < 10: RETURN n
        ELSE: RETURN (n mod 10) + digit.sum (floor (n / 10))

FOR n IN {1..99}:
    IF prime (digit.sum (n**2)) AND prime (digit.sum (n**3)):
        WRITE n/
